products.title: Womens Vintage Sport Socks
products.body_html:
The Namath - named after Joe Namath, a New York Jets Quarterback. Made in a vintage cream yarn with Ivy Ellis's signature Ivy green heel and toe. Contains 86% cotton, 13% polyamide and 1% elastane for extra comfort and durability. Finished with a soft elasticated top in Ivy green, for extra hold.

One Size 4-7
